des:
Provides sightings of notable/rare birds in Ireland and the UK provided by ebird.org/explore
Works for counties and capital cities of Ireland and UK.

Try a listing for : 
- Alexa open Birdie Sightings.
- Alexa ask Birdie Sightings for county Dublin. (Kerry, Fife, Caerphilly ,Kent)
- Alexa ask Birdie Sightings for last Monday.
- Alexa ask Birdie Sightings for on Monday.
- Alexa ask Birdie Sightings for county Dublin last Monday. (Kerry, Fife, Caerphilly ,Kent)
